# FINANCIAL INDEBTEDNESS

Our Company and our Subsidiary have availed loans in the ordinary course of business for the purposes of meeting working capital requirements and for capital expenditure. Our Company has obtained the necessary consents and has notified the relevant lenders as required under the relevant loan documentation for undertaking activities, such as substantial change in its shareholding pattern, change in the constitution of our Company, which would adversely affect the interest of the lender and material change in the information provided by our Company to the lenders.

